title: OUT NOW: Erick The Architect Live on KEXP

description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Erick The Architect performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded April 17, 2024.

Songs:
Parkour
Ezekiel's Wheel
Beef Patty
Shook Up (Feat. FARR)
Liberate

Erick Elliot - Principal Vocals
Ugonnaya - Gogo
Chilaka - DJ/Playback
Heidi Jauregui - Keys, Bass, BGVs
Romeo Testa (FARR)
Linden Jay Berelowitz (FARR)

Host: Larry Mizell, Jr.
Audio Engineer & Audio Mixer: Kevin Suggs
Guest Audio Engineer: Jeffrey Harris
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Jonathan Jacobson & Luke Knecht
